flowchart LR
  user[User]
  proxy[Optional reverse proxy, Ingress, Gateway, or Tunnel]
  route[Docker port mapping or Kubernetes Service]
  app[HAAI application container]
  data[(Persistent /data storage)]

  user --> proxy
  proxy --> route
  route --> app
  app --> data

  subgraph Kubernetes
    ingress[Optional Ingress or Gateway]
    service[Kubernetes Service]
    pod[Application Pod]
    pvc[(PersistentVolumeClaim)]
    storage[User-selected StorageClass]
    ingress --> service --> pod --> pvc --> storage
  end
